title: -Elastic Neutron Scattering Measurements On 94-Pu-239 In The Energy Range Between 0.19 and 0.38 Mev.-

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Zeitschrift fuer Physik, Vol.228, p.286 (1969)

x4freetext: IN THE ENERGY RANGE BETWEEN 0.19 AND 0.38 MEV.-
3 MEV DE GRAAFF ACCELERATOR OF THE CBNM.
36 - 40 KEV ENERGY SPREAD DEPENDING ON TARGET.
.A SOLID CYLINDER OF 1.2 CM DIAMETER, 2.5 CM
HEIGHT AND A WEIGHT OF 54.803 G,
.THE PU-SAMPLE WAS CANNED IN A ZIRCALLOY CONTAINER,
AN IDENTICAL EMPTY CAN WAS USED TO SUBTRACT THE
SCATTERING CONTRIBUTION COMING FROM THE CONTAINER.
MEASURED AT 10 DIFFERENT ANGLES BETWEEN 25 AND 147
AN NE 102A PLASTIC SCINTILLATOR, 5.0 CM IN
DIAMETER AND 2.5 CM THICK, VIEWED FROM ONE SIDE BY TWO
